'''''Memories in a Bottle''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Amphoreus]] in the chapter [[Amphoreus Annals]].

==Steps==
# Talk to the honey brew manager to learn more about what is happening
# Search for Hysilens's priest
# Step onto the altar and try making another bottle of soul brew
# Find the spirit basin and see if you can discover the Titan's thoughts
# Return to the brewing area
# Step onto the altar and try making another bottle of soul brew
# Observe the new brewing area

